Quickstrike:




Quickstrike stretched a leg out and sat up from his bunk. With a few 
hours, he was rested to better performance in battle and command, 
what ever shall turn. He stood up, and walked out from his quarters. 
He went to the bridge to check who was there and if there was any 
thing there to do. Any commands or such. He looked around and walked 
to the command chair. He checked the monitors, each camera that was 
suplied to the internal and external parts of the ship. After he saw 
nothing wrong, no signs of Megatron or Hell Beast, which he was 
looking for, he turned away. 

For a moment, he checked his shoulder. It wasn't in the best shape. 
He managed to pop it back into place, but not very skillfully. He 
would have to make a visit to the CR room later.

He exited the room to explore the cooridors again, to get the hang of 
the vessle.
